Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,500)\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\b1\c&H00438FF1\fs50\fsp5\bord0\shad3\4c&H00899299\frz358.6\p1\pos(434.133,636.666)}m 44 -9 b 81 -9 81 48 44 48 b 7 48 7 -9 44 -9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先確定要帶的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,說到露營 需要的東西是…
